61
00:04:35,742 --> 00:04:37,871
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti menangis...,</font>

62
00:04:38,542 --> 00:04:39,842
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan duduklah.</font>

63
00:04:40,941 --> 00:04:43,071
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan menjadi kepala keluarga
