64
00:04:43,871 --> 00:04:45,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau akan bisa...</font>

65
00:04:46,412 --> 00:04:48,511
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjaga kakakmu jika kau sangat lemah?</font>

66
