76
00:06:04,811 --> 00:06:06,112
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kau manusia.</font>

77
00:06:08,871 --> 00:06:10,011
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kau...</font>

78
00:06:11,412 --> 00:06:13,342
<font color=#FFFF00>...manusia, bukan mesin.</font>

79
00:06:24,972 --> 00:06:26,542
<font color=#FFFF00>Berbagilah denganku.</font>

80
00:06:29,172 --> 00:06:30,771
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak selalu.</font>

81
00:06:33,742 --> 00:06:36,511
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya saat kau berjuang seperti ini.</font>

82
00:06:41,412 --> 00:06:42,542
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

83
00:06:45,412 --> 00:06:46,641
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak membutuhkanmu.</font>

84
00:06:48,011 --> 00:06:50,311
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan terlibat dengan keluargaku lagi.</font>

85
00:06:51,172 --> 00:06:53,211
<font color=#FFFF00>Meskipun saudaraku memanggilmu...</font>

86
00:06:54,571 --> 00:06:57,112
<font color=#FFFF00>Meskipun ayahku sekarat atau...</font>

87
00:06:58,641 --> 00:07:00,441
<font color=#FFFF00>...meskipun sekarat...,</font>

88
00:07:02,871 --> 00:07:04,172
<font color=#FFFF00>...jangan pernah...</font>

89
00:07:06,941 --> 00:07:08,711
<font color=#FFFF00>...terlibat lagi.</font>

90
00:07:58,141 --> 00:08:00,771
<font color=#FFFF00>Bujuklah dia sebisa mungkin.</font>

91
00:08:00,771 --> 00:08:03,242
<font color=#FFFF00>Suruh dia menghapus catatanku.</font>

92
00:08:03,242 --> 00:08:05,511
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah tidak bisa melakukan itu.
