107
00:08:46,841 --> 00:08:48,571
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sudah bertahun-tahun.</font>

108
00:08:49,341 --> 00:08:52,341
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, dia hampir selesai melunasi bank.</font>

109
00:08:56,811 --> 00:08:58,811
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku meminjam dari rentenir juga.</font>

110
00:08:59,172 --> 00:09:00,311
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

111
00:09:01,241 --> 00:09:05,471
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin kembali, melunasi hutangku...,</font>

112
00:09:06,142 --> 00:09:08,772
