<font color=#FFFF00>...dan hutangku semakin bertambah.</font>

115
00:09:16,471 --> 00:09:19,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengarkan aku baik-baik, Woo Jae.</font>

116
00:09:21,412 --> 00:09:23,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak berguna dan pecundang...,</font>

117
00:09:23,872 --> 00:09:26,912
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku tetap ayahmu.</font>

118
00:09:27,471 --> 00:09:30,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mungkin tidak bisa memberimu warisan...,</font>

119
00:09:30,611 --> 00:09:34,542
