142
00:11:23,012 --> 00:11:26,042
<font color=#FFFF00>Young Eun.
/ <i>Aku tidak akan sembuh.</i></font>

143
00:11:27,111 --> 00:11:29,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini hanya membeli waktu.</font>

144
00:11:30,772 --> 00:11:33,471
