157
00:13:02,071 --> 00:13:04,012
<font color=#FFFF00>...ataupun menyukaiku.</font>

158
00:13:05,611 --> 00:13:08,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu membuatku senang
meskipun aku tahu semuanya.</font>

159
00:13:10,311 --> 00:13:12,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenyataan kalau...</font>

160
00:13:13,042 --> 00:13:16,912
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau datang sudah cukup
untuk membuatku bahagia.</font>

161
00:13:17,372 --> 00:13:18,642
<font color=#FFFF00>Berobatlah.</font>

162
00:13:21,611 --> 00:13:23,412
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak punya niat.</font>

163
00:13:23,412 --> 00:13:25,211
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau sangat sulit diatur?</font>

164
00:13:25,211 --> 00:13:26,471
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada gunanya.</font>

165
00:13:26,471 --> 00:13:29,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak mempertimbangkan orang-orang
