166
00:13:31,412 --> 00:13:34,372
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu membuatmu terluka?</font>

167
00:13:35,971 --> 00:13:37,711
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika aku mati..,</font>

168
00:13:38,772 --> 00:13:41,741
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau akan terluka juga?</font>

169
00:13:44,841 --> 00:13:46,971
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau tinggal denganku...</font>

170
00:13:50,071 --> 00:13:52,512
<font color=#FFFF00>...tanpa mencintai orang lain...,</font>

171
00:13:53,471 --> 00:13:55,012
<font color=#FFFF00>...jika kau berjanji...</font>

172
00:13:55,571 --> 00:13:57,941
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk tinggal hanya di sisiku...,</font>

173
00:13:59,571 --> 00:14:01,241
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan berobat.</font>

174
00:14:04,012 --> 00:14:05,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak mau?</font>

175
00:14:41,672 --> 00:14:44,172
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah selesai?
/ Hampir.</font>

176
00:14:44,711 --> 00:14:46,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa tidur karena pekerjaan.</font>

177
00:14:46,971 --> 00:14:48,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana denganmu?</font>

178
00:14:50,111 --> 00:14:51,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah kita makan sesuatu?</font>

179
00:14:52,512 --> 00:14:54,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mentraktir.</font>

180
00:15:08,971 --> 00:15:10,042
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanlah.</font>

181
00:15:20,172 --> 00:15:21,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita ubah grafiknya.</font>

182
00:15:25,571 --> 00:15:27,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah mengubahnya,
